@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iqvymw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.40 / v1 + 0.33)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.84 * tmp + 0.07)) - ((v0 + 0.74 * v1 + 0.79) / (tmp + 0.15 / v2 + 0.43)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.56 * v0 + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
